core/base.py
Vazifa: Barcha modellarga umumiy ustunlar beradi

Nima qiladi:
- Base      → barcha modellar shu dan meros oladi
- TimestampMixin → har modelga avtomatik qo'shadi:
    id         → har jadvalda asosiy kalit
    created_at → qachon yaratildi (server vaqti)
    updated_at → qachon o'zgartirildi (avtomatik)
    is_deleted → o'chirilganmi (soft delete)

Nima uchun alohida fayl:
- Takrorlanishni kamaytiradi
- 10 ta model = 0 ta takror
- Django da abstract = True bilan bir xil


----------------------------------------------------------

auth/models.py
Vazifa: PostgreSQL da jadvallar tuzilmasini belgilaydi

Nima qiladi:
- User         → xodimlar jadvali (waiter, chef)
- Table        → stollar jadvali
- TableSession → mijoz QR skanerlagan sessiya

Indexlar:
- ix_users_username          → login tezlashadi
- ix_users_role_active       → "barcha waiterlar" so'rovi tezlashadi
- ix_tables_number           → stol raqami tez topiladi
- ix_tables_qr_code          → QR skanerlanganda tez topiladi
- ix_table_sessions_token    → sessiya tez topiladi
- ix_table_sessions_table_active → "bu stolda sessiya bormi?" tezlashadi

Django da o'rnini bosadi:
- models.Model → Base + TimestampMixin


--------------------------------------------------------------------------

database.py
Vazifa: PostgreSQL ga async ulanish

Nima qiladi:
- engine           → PostgreSQL ga "yo'l" ochadi
- pool_size=10     → 10 ta doimiy ulanish
- max_overflow=20  → pik vaqtda +20 ta ulanish
- pool_recycle     → 30 daqiqada ulanish yangilanadi
- AsyncSessionLocal → har so'rovda session yaratadi
- get_db()         → har endpointga session beradi,
                     xato bo'lsa rollback qiladi

Django da o'rnini bosadi:
- settings.py DATABASES → DATABASE_URL
- Django session boshqaruvi → get_db()


--------------------------------------------------------------

auth/schemas.py
Vazifa: Brauzerdan kelgan ma'lumotni tekshiradi

Nima qiladi:
- UserCreate   → yangi xodim qo'shganda:
                 full_name (min 3), username (min 3),
                 password (min 6), role (waiter/chef)

- UserLogin    → login qilganda:
                 username + password

- Token        → login muvaffaqiyatli bo'lganda:
                 access_token + token_type qaytaradi

- TokenData    → JWT decode bo'lganda:
                 token ichidan username + role olinadi

- UserResponse → user ma'lumoti ko'rsatganda:
                 id, full_name, username, role, is_active
                 ⚠️ password HECH QACHON qaytarilmaydi

Django da o'rnini bosadi:
- serializers.py → schemas.py (Pydantic)


------------------------------------------------------------------------

auth/crud.py
Vazifa: Database bilan barcha amallar

Nima qiladi:
- hash_password()         → "1234" → "$2b$12$..."
                            parol ochiq saqlanmaydi
- verify_password()       → login da parol tekshiradi
- get_user_by_username()  → username bo'yicha topadi
                            is_deleted=True bo'lsa topilmaydi
                            is_active=False bo'lsa topilmaydi
- create_user()           → yangi xodim yaratadi,
                            parolni hashlab saqlaydi
- authenticate_user()     → username + parol tekshiradi,
                            to'g'ri bo'lsa user qaytaradi

Django da o'rnini bosadi:
- User.objects.get()    → get_user_by_username()
- User.objects.create() → create_user()
- authenticate()        → authenticate_user()
- make_password()       → hash_password()
- check_password()      → verify_password()


----------------------------------------------------------------

auth/router.py
Vazifa: Endpointlar — brauzerdan so'rov qabul qiladi

Nima qiladi:
- POST /auth/register → yangi waiter/chef qo'shadi
                        username band bo'lsa xato qaytaradi

- POST /auth/login    → username + parol keladi
                        to'g'ri bo'lsa JWT token qaytaradi
                        noto'g'ri bo'lsa 401 xato

- GET  /auth/me       → token keladi
                        token decode bo'ladi
                        o'z ma'lumotlarini qaytaradi

JWT:
- SECRET_KEY   → token imzolash uchun
- ALGORITHM    → HS256
- Muddati      → 60 daqiqa

Django da o'rnini bosadi:
- urls.py + views.py → router.py (ikkalasi bitta faylda)
- @login_required    → Depends(get_current_user)

main.py
Vazifa: Bosh fayl — hamma narsani birlashtiradi

Nima qiladi:
- lifespan         → ilova ishga tushganda jadvallar
                     yaratiladi (Base.metadata.create_all)
                     ilova to'xtaganda DB ulanish yopiladi
- FastAPI()        → ilova yaratiladi
- include_router() → auth router biriktiriladi
- GET /            → "RestoAI ishlayapti ✅"

Django da o'rnini bosadi:
- settings.py    → main.py (sozlamalar)
- urls.py asosiy → app.include_router()
- manage.py      → uvicorn main:app

So'rovlar yo'li — to'liq:
REGISTER:
Brauzer → POST /auth/register
              ↓
          router.py — so'rov qabul qiladi
              ↓
          schemas.py (UserCreate) — tekshiradi
              ↓
          crud.get_user_by_username — band emasmi?
              ↓
          crud.create_user — hashlab saqlaydi
              ↓
          schemas.py (UserResponse) — qaytaradi
              ↓
          Brauzer ← { id, full_name, username, role }

LOGIN:
Brauzer → POST /auth/login
              ↓
          router.py — so'rov qabul qiladi
              ↓
          schemas.py (UserLogin) — tekshiradi
              ↓
          crud.authenticate_user — username + parol
              ↓
          create_access_token — JWT yaratadi
              ↓
          Brauzer ← { access_token, token_type }

ME:
Brauzer → GET /auth/me + token
              ↓
          router.py — token qabul qiladi
              ↓
          get_current_user — token decode
              ↓
          crud.get_user_by_username — topadi
              ↓
          Brauzer ← { id, full_name, username, role }

